<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/10766647/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            中国历史的教训的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 12 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5718147">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5718147/" class="title-link">应该大力推广</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5718147"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/laobai/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1009635-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/laobai/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">LaoBai</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-29"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-29 00:40:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5718147_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我个人正在读这本书。此书的目标也基本赞同，但过程似乎有些用力过猛，矫枉过正。 但考虑此书观点的正确性（主观判断）和稀缺性（首版印数只有5000），还是应该大力推广和传播。 道理不辨不明，真理不检验不知道是否是真理。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 2没用</span>
